spec_data.Name: texlive-underoverlap
spec_data.Description:
The package overcomes TeX's inherent limitations in commands
that place decorations (such as braces) at arbirary positions
over and under expressions, overlapping as necessary.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 07:44:54 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Position decorations over and under expressions
